### Atualizar progresso da jornada - Em andamento
# PUT /jornadas/{jornada_id}/progresso → Cria ou atualiza o progresso (upsert)
# 
# Requer header: X-User-Id
# Response esperado (200): ProgressoDTO
# 
# Status possíveis: not-started, in-progress, completed, abandoned

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

PUT {{baseUrl}}/jornadas/jornada-001/progresso
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user123

{
  "jornadaId": "jornada-001",
  "status": "in-progress",
  "bestErrors": 2,
  "completedAt": null,
  "currentQuestionIndex": 3,
  "currentErrors": 1,
  "currentLives": 2,
  "lastActiveAt": 1720209591000,
  "bestTime": 45000
}
